{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i><strong>Adding this to your wishlist would be a great help to us!</strong></i></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544740/extras/EN_01.png?t=1737615738\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544740/extras/KakaoTalk_20241022_165350328__\uc0ac\uc6a9\uc790_\uc9c0\uc815_.png?t=1737615738\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Does that shape look like a hexagon to you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544740/extras/Hexagon.gif?t=1737615738\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shine the light to reveal its true form.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544740/extras/Line.png?t=1737615738\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544740/extras/EN_03.png?t=1737615738\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544740/extras/Lighting.gif?t=1737615738\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>&quot;THANKS, LIGHT.&quot;</strong> is a puzzle platformer game where you shine or absorb light to transform objects between 2D and 3D states.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don't judge objects by their silhouettes. Shine light to reveal the true form of the objects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544740/extras/Line.png?t=1737615738\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544740/extras/EN_04.png?t=1737615738\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544740/extras/Rotation.gif?t=1737615738\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Did you know that even cylinders have squares?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find the hidden shapes within each figure and solve parts of puzzles in ways only possible in <strong>&quot;THANKS, LIGHT.&quot;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544740/extras/Line.png?t=1737615738\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544740/extras/EN_05.png?t=1737615738\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544740/extras/Physics_original.gif?t=1737615738\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the 2D state, there are no physics,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">but in the 3D state, physics applies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use this characteristic to solve various physics puzzles by traversing between two and three dimensions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544740/extras/Line.png?t=1737615738\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544740/extras/EN_06.png?t=1737615738\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2544740/extras/story_original.gif?t=1737615738\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the mysterious space prepared by the self-proclaim